&lt;p&gt;Glossier is looking for a creative, community-first social media expert to support the development of ownable, best-in-class social strategy and social marketing campaigns.&lt;br&gt;This person will support the social team, reporting to the Senior Social Media Manager, and will be responsible for audience and engagement growth across all owned channels to drive brand awareness and advocacy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This will include the daily management of channel operations (content planning, calendar management, caption copywriting, analytical reporting), along with executing the social strategy for brand launches, in collaboration with cross-functional partners. The ideal candidate will be at the forefront of social trends and innovation and have a strong creative eye, as well as the ability to develop channel-by-channel goals and effectively measure success. You will play a key role in driving engagement, gathering feedback, and creating strategies to grow and strengthen our community. Additional responsibilities include: &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EXPECTATIONS.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6 Months&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The contribution of concepts and ideas for always-on content and campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross-channel execution with the ability to strategically plan engaging content and push innovation across channels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaboration and briefing cross-functional teams and external partners on opportunities to strategically feature content across owned social&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Light touch ad hoc content creation for Tik Tok, Instagram Stories, and Instagram, as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic social reporting that measures content performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Platform literacy so Glossier is able to stay on top of social media trends and identify moments for the brand to tap into&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;12 Months&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Development of a social dashboard with active insights to ensure we are learning and driving results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The proactive building and maintenance of the brand&#39;s online community by fostering meaningful interactions, monitoring social media sentiment and trends, and responding promptly to relevant comments and feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross-channel calendar management and ownership of social workstreams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
